FieldSet.description: Chassis: CMDB Class that stores information about frames that serve as the structural support for a computer system's electronic components. It can include information about physical elements that enclose other elements and provide definable functionality, such as a desktop computer, a processing node, an uninterruptible power supply (UPS), disk or tape storage, or a combination of such elements. This class corresponds to the DMTF CIM_Chassis class.
FieldSet.label: Chassis
